\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {S1}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {{\color {red}\sout {Validation and recovery of core annotation fields in the PanelAppRex dataset.}}} \textbf  {{\color {blue}\uwave {Validation of completeness for major annotation fields in the core dataset.}}} (A) {\color {red}\sout {Unique genes and }}{\color {blue}\uwave {Entry-level completeness of }}HGNC {\color {red}\sout {IDs }}{\color {blue}\uwave {identifiers }}before and after {\color {red}\sout {retrieving missing HGNC entries via }}{\color {blue}\uwave {recovery using }}Ensembl {\color {red}\sout {. (B) Availability }}{\color {blue}\uwave {biomaRt with HGNC symbol input, shown together with the total number }}of {\color {red}\sout {publication annotations for }}{\color {blue}\uwave {unique }}genes {\color {blue}\uwave {in the dataset as a reference}}. ({\color {red}\sout {C}}{\color {blue}\uwave {B}}) {\color {red}\sout {Unique genes and }}{\color {blue}\uwave {Entry-level completeness of }}Ensembl gene {\color {red}\sout {IDs }}{\color {blue}\uwave {identifiers }}before and after {\color {red}\sout {biomart-based }}recovery {\color {red}\sout {of missing }}{\color {blue}\uwave {using }}Ensembl {\color {red}\sout {IDs}}{\color {blue}\uwave {biomaRt with HGNC symbol input, shown together with the total number of unique genes in the dataset as a reference}}. ({\color {blue}\uwave {C) Entry-level completeness of publication annotations, shown as the number of gene-panel entries compared to those with at least one linked publication. (}}D) {\color {red}\sout {Gene }}{\color {blue}\uwave {Entry-level completeness of disease panel annotations, shown as the number of gene-panel }}entries with {\color {red}\sout {associated }}{\color {blue}\uwave {a gene and the number with a }}disease panel {\color {red}\sout {names}}{\color {blue}\uwave {name}}. (E) {\color {red}\sout {Gene }}{\color {blue}\uwave {Entry-level completeness of mode of inheritance annotations, shown as the number of gene-panel }}entries with {\color {red}\sout {annotated }}{\color {blue}\uwave {a gene and the number with a recorded mode of inheritance}}. (F) {\color {red}\sout {Gene }}{\color {blue}\uwave {Entry-level completeness of OMIM gene identifier annotations, shown as the number of gene-panel }}entries {\color {red}\sout {linked to }}{\color {blue}\uwave {with a gene and the number with }}an OMIM gene {\color {red}\sout {ID}}{\color {blue}\uwave {identifier}}. {\color {red}\sout {Each bar shows }}{\color {blue}\uwave {For all panels }}the {\color {red}\sout {count of }}{\color {blue}\uwave {percentages are calculated relative to total gene-panel }}entries{\color {red}\sout {with non-missing values }}{\color {blue}\uwave {, except }}for {\color {blue}\uwave {panels A and B where }}the {\color {red}\sout {respective field}}{\color {blue}\uwave {additional ``unique genes'' bars are calculated relative to the total number of unique genes}}. {\color {red}\sout {Updated fields (HGNC and Ensembl ID) reflect values recovered via external lookup using HGNC symbols. Percentage shows }}{\color {blue}\uwave {Entry-level refers to }}the {\color {red}\sout {complete recovery }}{\color {blue}\uwave {initial merging }}of {\color {red}\sout {coverage across features}}{\color {blue}\uwave {data from independent sources}}. }}{19}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
